<TEXT>
a commuter plane crashed and 
burned as it attempted to land in heavy fog tuesday and all seven 
people aboard were killed officials said 
the twinengine skylink airlines jet was on its second approach 
to the terracekitimat airport in northwest british columbia when 
it went down said christiane cote a spokesman for canadas 
transporation department the plane was carrying five passengers 
and two crew members 
what we know at this stage is the weather conditions were very 
