hundreds of east germans ignored 
spreading illness and pouring rain wednesday as they crowded into 
the west german embassy compound to press their demands to emigrate 
to the west 
i leave here only to the west or in a coffin said one woman 
newcomers scaled the fence of the embassy garden and refugees 
