thai denied the claims about vietnamese soldiers but 
acknowledged that guerrilla forces had taken some territory he 
said vietnamese troops left the area last year 
the announced vietnamese withdrawal has raised fears that 
cambodia will slide into a protracted civil war wars and bloody 
revolution have kept cambodia torn by conflict for the last 20 
years 
