anglofrench financier sir james goldsmith says 
the defensive restructuring proposed by bat industries plc is 
welcome but wont deter his hostile 22 billion bid for the british 
conglomerate 
bat on tuesday announced plans to sell its us retailing 
businesses spin off other operations and buy back 10 percent of 
