money in the bank 
starting wednesday any checking account customer who waits more 
than five minutes in a teller line at wells fargo bank branches in 
california will be credited 5 
for nearly two years weve had a program in our branches 
called five minute max in which our goal is to have customers 
reach the teller window in less than five minutes said don 
routh vice president in charge of the program 
we were the first california bank to develop this program and 
now we are the first to guarantee consistently fast service to our 
customers 
under the program a customer waiting more than five minutes 
will be given a guarantee form to turn in to a bank employee 
the branch will keep the form and add 5 to the customers checking 
account 
